id: CMP-telemetry
kind: component
name: Telemetry listener
status: draft
conformance_level: structural
level: subsystem
path: CMP-mission-computer / CMP-telemetry
description: Subscribes to MAVLink messages on UDP port 14552 and maintains a running state snapshot (position, altitude, heading, airspeed, mode). Also buffers raw messages for the event monitor to inspect for waypoint_reached, altitude_reached, and mode_changed triggers.
parent: CMP-mission-computer
port: state_out (provided IFC-telemetry)
